  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You take a relaxed stance drawing your weapon back and preparing for a full force attack. You spend your turn preparing this attack until the beginning of your next turn. You cannot take a bonus action or reaction after using this jutsu.</p><p>At the start of your next turn, you fire with full force. All creatures in a line 5 feet wide and 100 feet long originating from you must make a Dexterity saving throw at disadvantage, taking your [Weapon's damage] + 6d12 damage of your weapon's type.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above A-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, and the Save DC of this jutsu by +1</p>",
